{"tid":1382982,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「終極跪求」致咁多位上唔到前線嘅在職人士","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T18:31:16.000Z","uid":98507,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"acfbdd855b3309e3b7470457632101a4a4c325c1","tid":1382982,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"你地有各種責任在身<br />\n所以未能夠上前線，人之常情<br />\n你地亦唔係咩都冇做<br />\n會幫手出錢買物資，課金眾籌<br />\n好多謝你地<br />\n決戰當日<br />\n你地無論係企喺後面做和理非<br />\n定抑或喺屋企睇直播<br />\n相信見到年青人與警方對峙嘅場面<br />\n都會好痛心<br />\n點解企喺佢地前面嘅唔係我？<br />\n點解身為大人只可以匿喺佢地後面？<br />\n但人大左係會有包袱，大家都明<br />\n<br />\n到左呢刻<br />\n好坦白呢場運動就黎輸<br />\n今日國務院講到明會全力支持警隊<br />\n意味往後嘅抗爭<br />\n警方唔會再有保留<br />\n我地嘅年輕人將來<br />\n要受傷嘅受傷、要被捕嘅被捕...<br />\n繼續咁樣同警方玩落去<br />\n我地贏定輸，好明顯<br />\n<br />\n大人真係幫唔到手咩？顯然唔係<br />\n8月5號，好需要你地企出黎罷工<br />\n罷工，係唯一一條唔使流血<br />\n又有打擊性嘅抗爭手段<br />\n小貓三四隻罷工，公司當然會秋後算帳<br />\n但夠多人，就會凝聚成一種力量<br />\n多人去做同一件事，就會有合理性<br />\n<br />\n走在前線嘅人，係犧牲緊佢地嘅未來<br />\n一當場被捕，等住佢地嘅就係用年以計嘅刑罰<br />\n我地罷工，都只不過係扣人工(當然要夠多人)<br />\n同埋聽一陣閒言閒語<br />\n如果連咁都做唔到，呢場運動已經好難贏<br />\n因為我地搶唔返話事權，冇能力同政府叫板<br />\n<br />\n我跪求各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8月5號，一齊罷工<br />\n為左呢場運動<br />\n為左前線手足<br />\n為左我地嘅自由<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"547527aad2293fee644e019843964d553b1d91bc","tid":1382982,"uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"721 上環開槍開到放題咁<br />\n呢日之後，開槍冇再手軟過<br />\n728，警方多次用突擊戰術生禽前線手足<br />\n相信下次、下下次、下下下次都會用呢招<br />\n手足會越黎越少，出黎嘅人都會越黎越少<br />\n咁樣運動就會完結<br />\n中共亦會加速中港同化<br />\n同埋慢慢清算我地<br />\n現時反cup手段<br />\n除左唔知幾時先有嘅外國勢力<br />\n或者政府搵返比狗擔走嘅良心<br />\n就係得返罷工<br />\n我跪求咁多位，企出黎一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比敵人睇下我地嘅決心<br />\n<br />\n我已經決定由8月5日開始無限期罷工<br />\n直到運動完結<br />\n無論最後贏定輸，我會與你們同在"},{"pid":"00a277abaae957af10b74890034b5998da71f0f5","tid":1382982,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:33:11.000Z","msg":"先前有巴打提出8月5前搞一個罷工集會<br />\n比一d冇決心嘅人知道有幾多同路人<br />\n如果唔夠時間<br />\n不如提意有號召力嘅組織(eg.民陣)搞一個投票<br />\n睇下有幾多人響應<br />\n人數越多，越容易說服人罷工<br />\n<br />\n大家加油"},{"pid":"fb4eb9482901ce9f8927169bbb8cb8d536a9085a","tid":1382982,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5125a987541392260bf0a90fde8eb47a2c1255e","tid":1382982,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb4eb9482901ce9f8927169bbb8cb8d536a9085a","tid":1382982,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750a58b5ea687d1bbc80da4ad900ec18eb81a1c8","tid":1382982,"uid":58616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:05:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81bd77511b146a4ef6332d051f6c24c1d0b22a35","tid":1382982,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日<span style=\"color: red;\">中國</span>國務院講到明會全力支持警隊</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ce63159665b9b484ba7194f4aec01615db25fed3","tid":1382982,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:36:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bfce389706a7ce42df9b9a3652e6c285215cc30","tid":1382982,"uid":269285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4N9vVVt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4N9vVVt.jpg&h=a2e027d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4BeC8P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4BeC8P.jpg&h=fe9350ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zcL3wtQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzcL3wtQ.jpg&h=7a68439a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cR9Dknb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcR9Dknb.jpg&h=0cadf89f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gR7NdHc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgR7NdHc.jpg&h=d2d55c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Kz0yHd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Kz0yHd.jpg&h=d7daa2a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0b38df30f47bf83f977ac1d6a81d0defeda90e7","tid":1382982,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:18:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe4f8cd51f6457fb69c015154bb9b6fbf71456a7","tid":1382982,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:31:16.000Z","msg":"其實每次等咁耐先開波係因為佢地要等齊人做deployment<br />\n<br />\n唔好set block死守, 要好似捉圍棋抄小路反包圍"}]}